 adsorbate dependent turn-on temperature and electric field noise\nmagnitude, and also discuss the model's failure to reproduce the measured\n1/$\\omega$ noise frequency scaling with a single adsorbate species. We suggest\nfuture research directions for improved, quantitatively predictive models based\non extensions of the present framework to multiple interacting adsorbates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Oct 2018 06:06:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Apr 2019 19:26:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-04"}
